WEBVTT

00:11.340 --> 00:13.250
Now, let's see.

00:13.260 --> 00:15.290
Yeah, a few of the red ones,
please.

00:15.300 --> 00:17.860
Special someone, sir?
None more so.

00:20.820 --> 00:23.650
They say "truest love", red
tulips. Did you know that?

00:23.660 --> 00:24.850
No, I didn't.

00:24.860 --> 00:27.090
For every bloom a meaning,
sir, and every colour too.

00:27.100 --> 00:29.370
Might the lady care for
another?

00:29.380 --> 00:31.060
Yeah. Yeah, she likes these.

00:33.420 --> 00:35.500
Love forever lasting.

00:36.940 --> 00:40.210
Go on, then, let's have a
couple of the yellow ones,
then I'm off.

00:40.220 --> 00:42.820
Well, girl? What meaning these?

00:45.140 --> 00:46.500
Love without hope.

00:50.620 --> 00:52.420
It's only bloody flowers, innit?

